Key Match Events: Scott Edwards scored 68 runs, Wesley Barresi scored 41 runs for Netherlands
Mehidy Hasan Miraz, Mahmudullah, Mustafizur Rahman scored 35, 20, 20 runs respectively for Bangladesh
Paul van Meekeren took 4 wickets, Bas de Leede picked 2 wickets, while Colin Ackermann, Logan van Beek, and Aryan Dutt clinched one wicket each for Netherlands
Bangladesh all out at 142 runs, Netherlands won by 87 runs
Post-Match Reflections: Paul van Meekeren became the 'Player of the Match'
